         "challengeType":"horizontal"
      },
      {
         "id":"e753dc21-2544-4517-b66d-052898d6d9fb",
         "title":{
            "en":"Let's gear up!"
         },
         "description":{
            "en":"If the drive gear is two times bigger than the follow gear, it will double its speed, so the wheel will run twice as fast. In other words, with one spin of the handle our wheel will run two full circles.\n40/20=2\n2x20=40"
